data.title: Discworld
data.meta_description: List - Free download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read online for free. This document contains a list of over 200 books by various authors, primarily in the science fiction and fantasy genres. The list includes many series such as Piers Anthony's Xanth series (28 books), Terry Brooks' Shannara series (over 20 books), and Glen Cook's Garrett P.I. series (10 books). It also includes classic works by authors like Isaac Asimov, Dan Brown, and Roald Dahl. The document provides titles and file formats for each book.
